---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Instituto Saber Global | Pós-Graduação Internacional" currentPage="inicio">

<!-- [SEÇÃO 1: HERO] -->
<section class="relative pt-24 pb-16 md:pt-48 md:pb-32 px-6 overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">
<div class="z-10 text-center lg:text-left">
<h1 data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 100ms;" class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter text-on-background leading-[1.1] mb-6">
Sua Pós-Graduação Internacional com Suporte no Brasil.
</h1>
<p data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 400ms;" class="text-lg md:text-xl text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0">
Conectamos profissionais brasileiros a Mestrados e Doutorados de excelência na Universidad Del Sol (UNADES). Formação de alto nível com acompanhamento personalizado e foco no seu desenvolvimento global.
</p>
<div data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 700ms;" class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4">
<a href="/programas" class="w-full sm:w-auto justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-green-500/30 transition-all flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">school</span>
Conhecer Programas
</a>
<a href="/contato" class="w-full sm:w-auto justify-center bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-blue-700 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-blue-600/30 transition-all flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">support_agent</span>
Falar com um Consultor
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative" data-animate="zoom-in" style="transition-delay: 300ms;">
<div class="absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
<div class="relative rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden perspective-img shadow-2xl shadow-primary/20">
<img class="w-full h-auto max-h-[600px] object-contain bg-surface-container-lowest" alt="Universidad Del Sol - UNADES, parceira do Instituto Saber Global" src="/images/unades-nova.png" />
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/30 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- [SEÇÃO 2: QUEM SOMOS] -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-32 bg-surface-container-low relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Watermark Logo -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none flex items-center justify-center opacity-5">
    <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" class="w-full max-w-3xl object-contain drop-shadow-2xl" />
  </div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-20 items-center text-center lg:text-left">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <h2 data-animate="fade-right" class="text-sm font-bold text-tertiary uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-6">Quem Somos</h2>
        <h3 data-animate="fade-right" style="transition-delay: 100ms;" class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-on-surface tracking-tight mb-8">
          Instituto de Educação Saber Global:
          <br class="hidden lg:block"/>
          <span class="text-primary-container">Conectando Você ao Mundo.</span>
        </h3>
      </div>
      <div class="lg:col-span-7" data-animate="fade-left" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
        <div class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Sediado em Fortaleza (CE), o Instituto Saber Global nasceu para democratizar o acesso à educação internacional. Atuamos como o elo entre sua carreira e as melhores oportunidades acadêmicas no exterior, oferecendo suporte administrativo e pedagógico completo. Nossa missão é garantir que a distância geográfica não seja uma barreira para o seu doutorado ou mestrado.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- [SEÇÃO 3: NOSSOS PILARES] -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6 bg-surface">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center mb-12 md:mb-16" data-animate="fade-up">
<p class="text-tertiary font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-4">Excelência Acadêmica</p>
<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-on-background">Fundamentos de Nossa Atuação</h2>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<div data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 100ms;" class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-on-surface/5 group">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-fixed rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-on-primary-fixed mb-8 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-on-primary transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">school</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Pós-Graduação Stricto Sensu</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Programas de Mestrado e Doutorado internacionais, com foco especial na parceria com a Universidad Del Sol (UNADES - Paraguai).</p>
</div>
<div data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 250ms;" class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-on-surface/5 group">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-fixed rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-on-secondary-fixed mb-8 group-hover:bg-secondary group-hover:text-on-secondary transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">trending_up</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Formação Continuada</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Cursos de atualização e aperfeiçoamento desenhados para as demandas reais do mercado de trabalho contemporâneo.</p>
</div>
<div data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 400ms;" class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-on-surface/5 group">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-tertiary-fixed rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-on-tertiary-fixed mb-8 group-hover:bg-tertiary group-hover:text-on-tertiary transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">verified_user</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Reconhecimento de Títulos</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Assessoria especializada sobre os trâmites legais brasileiros, orientando o aluno em toda a jornada junto à Plataforma Carolina Bori.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- [SEÇÃO 4: POR QUE NOS ESCOLHER?] -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6 bg-primary text-on-primary relative overflow-hidden">
<!-- Background Animations -->
<div class="absolute top-[-20%] left-[-10%] w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[#1ca1ff] opacity-10 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse pointer-events-none" style="animation-duration: 6s;"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-[-20%] right-[-10%] w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[#42a8f5] opacity-20 rounded-full blur-[150px] animate-pulse pointer-events-none" style="animation-duration: 9s;"></div>
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
<div class="mb-12 md:mb-16 text-center md:text-left flex flex-col md:block items-center" data-animate="fade-up">
<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight mb-4">Por Que Nos Escolher?</h2>
<div class="h-1.5 w-24 rounded-full" style="background-color: #f5a623;"></div>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
<div data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 100ms;" class="bg-[#185880] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-transparent flex flex-col transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-black/30 group">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-fixed rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-on-primary-fixed mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-on-primary transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">handshake</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Parceria Institucional</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">Convênio oficial com a UNADES para cursos como Gestão em Saúde Pública.</p>
</div>
<div data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 250ms;" class="bg-[#185880] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-transparent flex flex-col transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-black/30 group">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-secondary-fixed rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-on-secondary-fixed mb-6 group-hover:bg-secondary group-hover:text-on-secondary transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">event_available</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Flexibilidade</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">Modalidades que respeitam sua rotina profissional.</p>
</div>
<div data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 400ms;" class="bg-[#185880] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-transparent flex flex-col transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-black/30 group">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-tertiary-fixed rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-on-tertiary-fixed mb-6 group-hover:bg-tertiary group-hover:text-on-tertiary transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">gavel</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Transparência Total</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">Instituição devidamente registrada (CNPJ 63.421.082/0001-68) e comprometida com a ética educacional.</p>
</div>
<div data-animate="fade-up" style="transition-delay: 550ms;" class="bg-[#185880] p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-transparent flex flex-col transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-black/30 group">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary mb-6 group-hover:bg-green-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl">support_agent</span>
</div>
<h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-white">Atendimento Humanizado</h4>
<p class="text-sm text-blue-100 leading-relaxed">Suporte personalizado de Fortaleza para todo o Brasil.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!-- [SEÇÃO 5: CTA FINAL] -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-32 px-6">
<div data-animate="zoom-in" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-[#185880] rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-20 text-center shadow-2xl shadow-black/20 relative overflow-hidden">
<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
O próximo passo da sua carreira começa aqui.
</h2>
<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-blue-50/90 leading-relaxed mb-10 md:mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
Não deixe sua qualificação para depois. Estude em uma instituição internacional com o suporte de quem entende o cenário educacional brasileiro.
</p>
<a href="/contato" class="w-full sm:w-auto max-w-xs sm:max-w-none justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 text-white px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-12 py-4 md:py-5 rounded-2xl md:rounded-xl font-black text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-1 active:translate-y-0 hover:shadow-green-500/40 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-green-500/30 inline-flex items-center flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 md:gap-3 mx-auto text-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined hidden md:block text-2xl">rocket_launch</span>
<span>Quero Iniciar Minha Inscrição</span>
</a>
</div>
</section>

<!-- [SCROLL ANIMATIONS SCRIPT & STYLES] -->
<style is:global>
  /* Base animation setup */
  [data-animate] {
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }
  
  /* Reset hover duration speed */
  [data-animate]:hover {
    transition-duration: 150ms !important;
  }
  
  /* Initial states */
  [data-animate="fade-up"] { transform: translateY(40px); }
  [data-animate="fade-right"] { transform: translateX(-40px); }
  [data-animate="fade-left"] { transform: translateX(40px); }
  [data-animate="zoom-in"] { transform: scale(0.93); }
  
  /* Visible state */
  [data-animate].is-visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: none;
  }
</style>

<script>
  // Setup intersection observer on page load
  function initAnimations() {
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add('is-visible');
          // Unobserve to run the animation only once
          observer.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, { 
      threshold: 0.15, // Trigger when 15% visible
      rootMargin: "0px 0px -50px 0px" // Trigger slightly before it hits bottom of viewport
    });

    document.querySelectorAll('[data-animate]').forEach((el) => {
      observer.observe(el);
    });
  }

  // Run immediately
  initAnimations();
</script>

</Base>
